# Auto-deploy to Vercel

After making any change to this project, deploy to Vercel production before ending the turn.

## Workflow

1. Make the requested code change.
2. Run `npm run build` — fix any build errors before deploying.
3. Deploy with `vercel deploy --prod --yes` from the project root.
4. Report the production URL (`https://nmdcd.com`) and deployment inspect link.

## When to skip

- Question-only or review-only requests with no file edits.
- User explicitly says not to deploy.
- Build fails and cannot be fixed in the same turn — report the failure instead.

## Notes

- This project has no git remote; use the Vercel CLI, not `git push`.
- Do not commit unless the user asks.
